WEBVTT

00:00:01.053 --> 00:00:03.697
INTERVIEW WITH SARA ZISKROIT.

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:05.621
mir hobn

00:00:05.762 --> 00:00:07.140
geredt vegn

00:00:07.753 --> 00:00:11.122
selektsyes, vi azoy zey hobn oysgeklibn mentshn.

00:00:11.246 --> 00:00:12.101
v-

00:00:12.242 --> 00:00:14.953
men hot oysgeklibn mentshn

00:00:15.228 --> 00:00:17.905
tsu farshikn er- ergets andersh?

00:00:17.456 --> 00:00:21.973
ye de-, az me hot gedarft hobn mentshn tsu der arbet, azoy vi me, ho- hot men undz avekgeshikt tsu der arbet.

00:00:21.962 --> 00:00:24.254
hot men oykh geshikt mentshn

00:00:24.290 --> 00:00:24.971
in

00:00:24.971 --> 00:00:27.609
in lagern?

00:00:28.037 --> 00:00:29.837
ye, un ikh bin g-, ikh bin gegangen in lager.

00:00:29.623 --> 00:00:34.309
yo, ober v- e- oyb ir zaynt gegangen in lager zaynt ir shoyn nisht tsurikgekumen in geto?

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:34.714
NO.

00:00:35.327 --> 00:00:37.155
vos hot ir gevust

00:00:37.155 --> 00:00:40.074
vegn kontsentratsyes-lagern?

00:00:40.119 --> 00:00:42.763
oder lagern vu m'hot oysgeharget yidn?

00:00:43.055 --> 00:00:45.867
mir hobn gevust ober me me me hot zikh gornisht nit gekent helfn.

00:00:46.177 --> 00:00:47.639
ir hot yo gevust.

00:00:47.190 --> 00:00:50.931
yo, mir, mir hobn dokh nit, mir hobn zikh gornisht nit gekent helfn; me hot undz gerufn, zaynen mir gegangen.

00:00:50.278 --> 00:00:50.950
yo.

00:00:50.987 --> 00:00:52.290
do- dos veys ikh.

00:00:52.290 --> 00:00:55.169
hot ir gevust, hot ir gehert vegn AUSCHWITZ?

00:00:55.172 --> 00:00:58.530
vo- fun velkhe lagern hot ir yo gehert?

00:00:58.547 --> 00:01:03.013
mir hobn nit gehert fun keyne lagern, biz vanet, un derno-, az ikh bin arayn in lager hob ikh yemolt gehert.

00:01:02.698 --> 00:01:06.264
ober in geto hot ir nisht gevust di nemen fun lagern.

00:01:04.359 --> 00:01:04.927
ye.

00:01:05.335 --> 00:01:06.374
NO, NO.

00:01:06.292 --> 00:01:09.307
fun ayer bruder in Rusland hot ir gehert?

00:01:09.161 --> 00:01:09.881
neyn.

00:01:09.830 --> 00:01:10.303
neyn.

00:01:10.882 --> 00:01:12.002
iz ven,

00:01:12.030 --> 00:01:15.568
vi azoy hot men aykh oysgeklibn geyn tsu

00:01:15.641 --> 00:01:16.968
an arbets-lager?

00:01:17.345 --> 00:01:19.651
gants p-, m'hot (on)geshtelt mey- meydlekh,

00:01:20.568 --> 00:01:23.009
mir zaynen geven meydle- hobn zey genumen velkhe zey hobn gevelt.

00:01:23.083 --> 00:01:25.035
un vi azoy hot men zey oysgeklibn?

00:01:24.804 --> 00:01:28.578
der der der daytsh hot gezogt, er hot ongevizn mitn finger vemen yo un vemen nit.

00:01:28.128 --> 00:01:30.502
yo, ot, iz dos geven a

00:01:30.913 --> 00:01:35.092
ve- sheynkeyt tsi arbets- -meglekhkeytn?

00:01:33.475 --> 00:01:37.303
zey hobn, zey hobn efsher gefilt az der iz me- mer feik tsu der arbet UNK.

00:01:37.646 --> 00:01:39.530
vi alt zayt ir dan geven?

00:01:39.738 --> 00:01:41.133
bay zekhtsn yor gleyb ikh.

00:01:40.312 --> 00:01:41.010
yo.

00:01:41.010 --> 00:01:41.623
yo.

00:01:41.983 --> 00:01:45.234
iz vi az- aykh hot men aykh oysgeklibn.

00:01:44.663 --> 00:01:45.883
yo. fun Vidz.

00:01:45.678 --> 00:01:47.059
fun Vidz.

00:01:46.692 --> 00:01:47.161
ye.

00:01:47.062 --> 00:01:48.727
un vu hot men aykh geshikt?

00:01:48.716 --> 00:01:53.190
zey hobn undz avekgeshikt in a la- lager, un mir hobn dortn gearbet, ober ikh gedenk nit dem nomen fun dem lager.

00:01:52.108 --> 00:01:53.869
yo, ikh veys, ir hot mir gezogt.

00:01:53.897 --> 00:01:56.693
de-, vi vayt iz ge- der lager geven?

00:01:56.327 --> 00:01:58.442
kh'hob nit keyn anung; s'iz geven vayt. ikh hob keyn mol nit ge-

00:01:56.934 --> 00:01:59.122
NO, ikh meyn, vi lang hot aykh genum-

00:01:58.442 --> 00:02:00.860
kh'hob keyn mol nit gehert fun mayne eltern. dernokh,

00:02:01.068 --> 00:02:03.206
kh'hob ye, ikh hob gehert ersht ven m'hot

00:02:03.313 --> 00:02:07.712
gebrakht mayne, plutsling hot men gebrakht mayne eltern tsu mir, ober ikh bin ikh bin geven farshribn.

00:02:06.080 --> 00:02:06.918
-huh.

00:02:07.599 --> 00:02:08.285
yo.

00:02:08.426 --> 00:02:10.564
iz di vos hobn gehat mishpokhe

00:02:11.497 --> 00:02:15.238
in di lager, in lager, hobn zey di, di men- di mishpokhe geshikt tsu zey.

00:02:15.697 --> 00:02:16.219
yo.

00:02:16.219 --> 00:02:20.688
ober vi, vi azoy hot men aykh gefirt tsu d-, tsum arbets-lager?

00:02:20.407 --> 00:02:22.156
mit a, mit a, mit a ban.

00:02:21.808 --> 00:02:22.750
mit a ban.

00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:25.414
un vi lang zaynt ir geven oyfn, oyf der ban?

00:02:25.807 --> 00:02:27.911
oyfn ban a tog, tsvey.

00:02:28.085 --> 00:02:29.480
vos far a ban?

00:02:30.009 --> 00:02:32.400
 a, a b- a, nit keyn pasazhir-ban.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.613
NO, far-, far-,

00:02:33.942 --> 00:02:35.158
a farmakhter ban.

00:02:34.613 --> 00:02:36.142
farmakhter ban..

00:02:36.219 --> 00:02:40.263
un vifl hot men oysgeklibn forn keyn arbets-lager?

00:02:41.315 --> 00:02:44.313
azoy geven fun far-, me hot genumen fun, fun farsheydene shtetlekh.

00:02:44.117 --> 00:02:45.411
yo.

00:02:44.606 --> 00:02:47.503
s'iz geven efsher bay a hundert froyen; dernokh hot (men) ongebrakht mener oykh.

00:02:47.913 --> 00:02:52.703
ah, eltere froyen oykh? NO, bloyz yunge meydlekh. yo.

00:02:49.563 --> 00:02:50.223
NO.

00:02:51.123 --> 00:02:52.783
yunge. keyn eltere hobn zey nit genumen.

00:02:52.740 --> 00:02:57.324
un ven ir zaynt ongekumen in lager, dos iz geven in nayntsn

00:02:57.380 --> 00:03:01.121
 g- velkhn yor iz, hot men aykh genumen in lager?

00:03:01.802 --> 00:03:04.210
in dray un fertsik, (tsu geven epes) tsvey un fertsik, UNK

00:03:03.759 --> 00:03:05.154
 yo.

00:03:05.295 --> 00:03:07.821
un ven ir zaynt ongekumen dortn

00:03:08.602 --> 00:03:13.878
vos gedenkt ir, v- vos hot ir gezen in lager ven ir zayn- dem tog vos ir zaynt aroys fun ban?

00:03:13.462 --> 00:03:17.197
vos hobn mir gezen in lager? gants poshet, s'iz geve-, s'iz geven gemakht palatkes

00:03:17.197 --> 00:03:18.016
un s'iz geven m-

00:03:18.016 --> 00:03:19.447
mir zaynen geshlofn oyfn shney.

00:03:19.993 --> 00:03:21.675
dernokh hobn zey gemakht barakn.

00:03:22.524 --> 00:03:23.846
un mir flegn geyn br-

00:03:23.846 --> 00:03:25.930
brukirn hay-, di vegn

00:03:25.930 --> 00:03:27.142
bay di vegn hobn mir gearbet.

00:03:26.945 --> 00:03:28.779
ir hot gemakht

00:03:28.447 --> 00:03:29.268
vegn.

00:03:29.038 --> 00:03:31.361
vegn. mener un froyen?

00:03:31.502 --> 00:03:32.222
ye.

00:03:31.805 --> 00:03:34.128
vos, ir hot gedarft,

00:03:34.286 --> 00:03:35.833
leygn tsement?

00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:37.406
NO, shteyner. mit b-

00:03:36.665 --> 00:03:37.621
shteyner.

00:03:37.406 --> 00:03:40.490
in m- in Poyln hot men gesh- gebrukirt mit shteyner.

00:03:41.238 --> 00:03:43.159
tsebrokhene shteyner oder

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:44.600
ye, shtiklekh shteyner.

00:03:44.225 --> 00:03:46.329
shtiker, ver hot zey tsebrokhn?

00:03:46.824 --> 00:03:48.286
s'iz gekumen a- m'hot gebrakht.

00:03:48.123 --> 00:03:51.087
andere, andere mentshn hobn gearbet bay di sh-

00:03:50.216 --> 00:03:54.170
dernokh hobn zey zikh, hobn zey, hot, mir, ikh tsef- UNK oysgefunen

00:03:54.170 --> 00:03:55.543
az mir kenen shtrikn.

00:03:56.527 --> 00:03:57.314
flegn

00:03:57.455 --> 00:04:03.609
flegn zey, flegn zey, ah, flegn di daytshn undz arayngebn tsu a p- a polyak ver se hot gevelt shtikn, hobn mir gekrogn esn.

00:04:03.665 --> 00:04:05.282
yedn tog hobn mir zikh (gedarft) UNK

00:04:05.282 --> 00:04:07.569
tsurikvayzn, di un di sho kumen tsum

00:04:07.569 --> 00:04:08.807
plats vu m'hot gearbet.

00:04:08.998 --> 00:04:11.811
un zey flegn krign far dem batsolt oder esn

00:04:12.204 --> 00:04:12.958
besere.

00:04:13.031 --> 00:04:13.768
yo.

00:04:14.617 --> 00:04:16.856
de- vu hot men aykh geleygt

00:04:17.250 --> 00:04:19.423
shlofn, un vu hot ir gelebt

00:04:19.442 --> 00:04:20.736
in di lagern?

00:04:20.709 --> 00:04:24.081
vu hot men undz geleygt shlofn? in, in, fr- fr- (frier) zaynen mir geshlofn in a

00:04:24.081 --> 00:04:25.918
kimat oyfn shney UNK untergebet.

00:04:26.210 --> 00:04:27.110
dernokh hobn mir

00:04:27.110 --> 00:04:31.082
dernokh iz geven, dernokh hot men gemakht barakn, hot men gemakht azoyne sh- shenikes

00:04:31.762 --> 00:04:33.123
ober s'iz geven etlekhe shtok.

00:04:32.893 --> 00:04:33.675
-huh.

00:04:33.703 --> 00:04:37.950
un vifl m- meydlekh hobn geshlofn oyf eyn shenik?

00:04:37.803 --> 00:04:39.384
a sakh. oyf eyn shenik?

00:04:39.828 --> 00:04:40.700
a sakh.

00:04:41.229 --> 00:04:42.939
s'iz geven epes untergebet, shtroy.

00:04:42.967 --> 00:04:44.767
ikh veys nit afile tsu s'iz geven a shenik.

00:04:44.486 --> 00:04:45.201
yo.

00:04:45.201 --> 00:04:48.581
un oyfn shney vu m'hot aykh geleygt shlofn iz geven

00:04:49.093 --> 00:04:52.828
hot ir gehat a a dakh, a a a TENT, a

00:04:52.451 --> 00:04:53.205
a TENT.

00:04:52.839 --> 00:04:53.815
a TENT.

00:04:53.586 --> 00:04:53.935
ye.

00:04:53.852 --> 00:04:54.389
-huh.

00:04:54.389 --> 00:04:58.317
un vi lang hot genumen boyen di, di budkes?

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:02.334
zey hobn gebrakht budkes, zey hobn avekgeshtelt. aza groyse mit, mit (budke UNK).

00:05:01.884 --> 00:05:04.345
 un iz ge- m'hot es geheyt?

00:05:04.345 --> 00:05:05.321
geheytsn?

00:05:04.820 --> 00:05:07.008
ye, s'iz geven an eyvele, vu UNK heytsn.

00:05:05.867 --> 00:05:06.688
aha.

00:05:06.845 --> 00:05:08.358
un vu hot ir gegesn?

00:05:08.769 --> 00:05:12.875
zey fle-, esn, ver hot dir gegebn esn? m'hot gegebn eyn mol in tog esn. ba- bay nakht (oybe zey kumen)

00:05:12.903 --> 00:05:14.267
hot hot men gegebn

00:05:14.267 --> 00:05:18.163
hot men gegebn a bisl vaser dortn, me, oyb s'iz geven in vaser a kartofl.

00:05:18.827 --> 00:05:22.601
un vi vayt hot ir gedarft geyn tsu der arbet?

00:05:21.864 --> 00:05:23.698
nit vayt, vayl m'iz gegangen tsu fus.

00:05:23.771 --> 00:05:24.862
tsu fus.

00:05:26.167 --> 00:05:26.971
ah

00:05:27.129 --> 00:05:33.766
hot ir gehat andere fraynd dortn, mentshn vo- fun ayer shtetl vos zaynen g- meydlekh vos ir hot hot gekent?

00:05:32.208 --> 00:05:34.346
vo- s'iz geven fun mayn, mayn shtetl, ye.

00:05:33.766 --> 00:05:34.531
-huh.

00:05:35.269 --> 00:05:35.893
un

00:05:35.893 --> 00:05:36.804
ver i-

00:05:36.804 --> 00:05:40.742
gedenkt ir efsher di kapos, hobn ze-, ir hot gehat kapos dortn?

00:05:40.173 --> 00:05:42.170
ye, eyne i- nor di Kh-

00:05:42.170 --> 00:05:43.762
ikh gedenk nor di eyne, Khave.

00:05:43.667 --> 00:05:44.474
Khave.

00:05:44.474 --> 00:05:46.710
dort, zi iz geven in arbets-lager?

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:47.750
ye, (fun) Oshmene.

00:05:46.755 --> 00:05:49.587
un zi iz geven fun ayer shtot, oder fun

00:05:48.712 --> 00:05:49.685
fun Oshmene.

00:05:49.587 --> 00:05:50.481
fun Oshm-

00:05:51.139 --> 00:05:54.832
vi azoy zaynen mentshn oysgekumen tsvishn zikh?

00:05:55.023 --> 00:05:56.142
di di meydlekh?

00:05:56.762 --> 00:05:59.763
me m'hot nit gehat vos nit oystsukumen. vos vos hobn mir gehat?

00:05:58.618 --> 00:05:59.135
ye,

00:05:59.765 --> 00:06:01.768
mir hobn gornisht nit gehat, hobn mir gornisht nit gedarft.

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:05.159
un di kapo iz geven gut tsu aykh tsi shlekht?

00:06:04.828 --> 00:06:05.885
vi a mol.

00:06:07.342 --> 00:06:10.509
(a fakt) iz a polyak hot a- opgegebn a feld

00:06:10.633 --> 00:06:12.551
mit, kh'veys nit vi me heyst dos.

00:06:12.708 --> 00:06:15.301
se zet oys vi retekher ober se heyst krutshke.

00:06:16.050 --> 00:06:18.525
s'iz aza zise, me flegt makhn in Poyln fun dem

00:06:18.615 --> 00:06:19.498
tsimes.

00:06:20.325 --> 00:06:23.860
hot er es opgegebn, un er hot gezogt az er git (ir) op far dem, far di mentshn

00:06:23.860 --> 00:06:25.528
un zoln nemen un zoln esn.

00:06:25.668 --> 00:06:28.417
ober dernokh hot men es farbot- farbotn undz nemen

00:06:28.417 --> 00:06:30.186
vayl m'hot gekrogn disen-, disenterye.

00:06:32.992 --> 00:06:34.606
men hot aykh

00:06:34.815 --> 00:06:36.415
vi azoy hot men geshtroft

00:06:36.415 --> 00:06:37.289
mentshn?

00:06:39.641 --> 00:06:43.494
vi, vi hot men geshtroft? zey hobn, lemoshl, emetser iz (aroys UNK er iz gegangen)

00:06:43.522 --> 00:06:46.160
in dorf nokh a shtikl broyt tsu vos, hot men im avekgeshtelt a m-

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:47.938
a, hot men im opgegosn mit vaser

00:06:48.568 --> 00:06:49.997
un m- oyfn, oyfn

00:06:50.407 --> 00:06:51.518
un er iz geshtanen

00:06:51.521 --> 00:06:54.080
oyfn gas, hot men im avekgeshtelt oyf azoy fil un azoy fil shtundn.

00:06:55.740 --> 00:06:57.557
m'hot aykh a mol geshtroft?

00:06:57.107 --> 00:06:57.861
NO.

00:06:58.541 --> 00:07:00.442
m'hot meydlekh oykh geshtroft?

00:07:00.448 --> 00:07:02.501
meydlekh, nor meyn-, ikh hob gemeynt meydlekh.

00:07:01.832 --> 00:07:02.563
yo.

00:07:05.173 --> 00:07:08.419
hot ir gehat a kontakt mit mener

00:07:08.419 --> 00:07:09.740
in

00:07:09.915 --> 00:07:11.293
in arbets-lager?

00:07:10.944 --> 00:07:11.968
zeyer veynik.

00:07:12.902 --> 00:07:15.168
zaynen meydlekh geven mit mener

00:07:15.213 --> 00:07:18.194
iz dortn geven a fal vos mentshn ho-

00:07:17.289 --> 00:07:19.106
mir zaynen geven mit, mit daytshn.

00:07:18.757 --> 00:07:23.544
yo, mit daytshn, hobn meydlekh gehat epes tsu ton mit di daytshn, hobn di daytshn...

00:07:22.740 --> 00:07:24.894
ye, s'iz geven andere vos hobn gehat tsu ton.

00:07:24.208 --> 00:07:24.956
ayo.

00:07:24.956 --> 00:07:25.969
un me- me-

00:07:25.969 --> 00:07:27.820
zey hobn gevoynt mit di daytshn?

00:07:27.684 --> 00:07:30.142
zey flegn kumen tsu zey bay nakht, kh'veys vi s'iz geven dortn.

00:07:28.848 --> 00:07:29.669
-huh.

00:07:30.466 --> 00:07:31.105
un

00:07:31.802 --> 00:07:35.171
gedenkt ir a fal vu s'iz geboyrn gevorn kinder?

00:07:35.362 --> 00:07:36.048
NO.

00:07:35.902 --> 00:07:36.538
NO.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:42.832
di kapo iz geven mit aykh di gantse tsayt?

00:07:43.445 --> 00:07:45.194
bay der arbet? ye.

00:07:44.137 --> 00:07:44.874
yo.

00:07:46.095 --> 00:07:46.849
un

00:07:47.917 --> 00:07:52.454
vi azoy hot ir z- gebitn di arbet tsu zayn, tsu shtrikn?

00:07:52.454 --> 00:07:53.852
m'hot aykh gebetn?

00:07:54.515 --> 00:07:55.170
di...

00:07:54.566 --> 00:07:56.315
OR hot ir zikh gemoldn?

00:07:55.207 --> 00:07:57.901
s'iz geven a daytsh eyner, hot geheysn KUNZE.

00:07:58.008 --> 00:07:59.001
un er iz geven

00:07:59.001 --> 00:08:02.525
zeyer, zeyer gut tsu (yidn). hot geflegt ganvenen esn un brengen undz.

00:08:03.257 --> 00:08:05.749
flegt er mir arayngeyn, er, er hot gevust az ikh ken shtrikn.

00:08:06.699 --> 00:08:11.362
a fakt az me, me, ikh hob geshtrikt oyf in di, in lager, flegt er (mir nokh) araynnemen di vol

00:08:11.362 --> 00:08:13.590
mitn sveter, flegt er nemen bay zikh in tash

00:08:13.635 --> 00:08:15.328
ober m'hot, ikh hob nit gekent, m'hot tomer

00:08:15.328 --> 00:08:17.325
kontrolirt men mir, hob ikh nit getort trogn.

00:08:18.292 --> 00:08:21.628
azoy, hot er undz arayngegebn tsu a po- polyak

00:08:21.971 --> 00:08:24.727
mir mit a kh- nokh eyne, un mir hobn geshtrikt far zey

00:08:24.727 --> 00:08:26.184
un zey hobn undz gegebn esn

00:08:26.325 --> 00:08:28.800
un er hot gekrogn batsolt, oder er hot gekrogn oykh epes esn.

00:08:28.890 --> 00:08:30.210
bronfn, ikh veys vos.

00:08:30.155 --> 00:08:31.331
 der daytsh?

00:08:31.086 --> 00:08:31.783
der daytsh, ye.

00:08:31.522 --> 00:08:34.166
der daytsh iz geven fun, fun vanen?

00:08:34.003 --> 00:08:36.394
fun di vos zey hobn gearbet mit undz bayn, oyfn veg.

00:08:36.078 --> 00:08:36.849
-huh.

00:08:36.905 --> 00:08:40.820
zey zaynen geven politsey, oder zey hobn aykh gehit, oder zey...

00:08:40.145 --> 00:08:41.201
zey hobn undz gehit.

00:08:40.984 --> 00:08:41.595
-huh.

00:08:41.765 --> 00:08:42.412
I SEE.

00:08:42.412 --> 00:08:50.096
un ir, ir, ir zaynt gegangen fun arbets-lager tsu dem poylishn, tsu di polyakn shtrikn?

