00:13:12.356 --> 00:13:13.788
z- ye, zey zaynen ongekumen

00:13:13.788 --> 00:13:15.793
zaynen gekumen in dem lager un hobn zey genumen.

00:13:17.587 --> 00:13:21.845
ve- un es iz geblibn ayer muter un di kinder, un ven zaynen, yo.

