KIESGRUBEN iz a, a QUARRY vu me, ah, makht tsement?

00:13:48.367 --> 00:13:48.938
NO.

00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:49.628
vos?

00:13:48.938 --> 00:13:51.197
s'iz geven, geven dortn azoy vi zamd.

00:13:52.130 --> 00:13:54.706
un dortn afile di polyakn hobn undz gezogt az mir zaynen

00:13:54.965 --> 00:13:59.088
di, di eltern hobn undz oysgekoyft. dos iz geven frier nokh, eyder m'hot genumen mayn foter.

00:13:59.133 --> 00:14:03.987
az di, az mir zaynen LUCKY az di, (mit) di eltern (hobn zey) zikh oysgekoyft, zey hobn batsolt far undz, vi zey zaynen gekumen fun Sh-

00:14:05.529 --> 00:14:08.628
fun Sventsya- hobn di polyakn gezogt az mir zayne ge-

00:14:08.735 --> 00:14:11.362
zeyer LUCKY vos zey hobn mir, zey hobn undz bafrayt.

00:14:11.452 --> 00:14:13.635
vayle z- zey hobn undz gevizn vi es lign

00:14:13.635 --> 00:14:16.290
me- m'hot gebrakht ahin mener, un di mener hobn zey oysgeharget.

00:14:17.021 --> 00:14:19.057
iz vu zaynt ir gef- ge-

00:14:19.232 --> 00:14:22.787
geven nokh ki- v- grobn KIESGRUBEN?

00:14:22.877 --> 00:14:23.580
hobn

00:14:23.687 --> 00:14:26.753
hobn undz di eltern, ven di eltern zaynen gekumen fun Sventsyan

00:14:26.859 --> 00:14:28.372
hobn zey nokh epes gehat

